{"tid":2118553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[TVB]抗疫要屯糧，一定要買啲壽桃牌喺屋企！！！","createTime":"2020-07-21T13:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T09:35:51.000Z","uid":183576,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ce78c0d02212f8280242b8952eb87db62789357a","tid":2118553,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:49:40.000Z","msg":"點解？因為佢啲麵<strong><span class=\"red\">防腐劑夠曬多囉，超出正常標準三成，保存得耐</span></strong>就算武肺肆虐到下年都無有怕！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />浸完林鄭啲閪水都仲食得呀屌你<br />\n<br />\n再者，情侶成日困響屋企，難免會有「親密少少既行為」，想避孕既大家可以食多兩包壽桃牌即食麵，因為佢既<strong><span class=\"red\">脫水菜包、調味油包含有接近可容忍上限既塑化劑，而攝取太多塑化劑係會影響生育</span></strong>既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />到時無限中出都不是夢<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，<strong><span class=\"red\">佢隻雞粉都好值得推介，因為佢直頭係濃縮納黎</span></strong>，每100克鈉含量達21,600毫克，即係咩？即係<strong><span class=\"red\">食9.3克就超出世衛建議上限</span></strong>囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啱曬你班連登鹹蟲<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"> <img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/109726150_155960432787003_2871471578792152369_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=-6u2T5pKgNgAX9SnSyO&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=a9afa16fcc1501d0d766292d5d4fd99b&amp;oe=5F3E0DF5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F109726150_155960432787003_2871471578792152369_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3D-6u2T5pKgNgAX9SnSyO%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3Da9afa16fcc1501d0d766292d5d4fd99b%26oe%3D5F3E0DF5&h=c7500b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【每日任務@ 21 Jul】<br />\n💎壽桃牌💎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sautaoHK/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FsautaoHK%2Fposts%2F&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=c477c7b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sautaoHK/posts/</a><br />\n<br />\n壽桃牌2016年響佛山里水鎮投資30億，建立「壽桃綠色民生食品城」，喔，即係中國製造扮「香港品牌」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</p><br />\n<em><span class=\"small\">Source: <br />\n2016年《全蛋麵防腐劑超標三成》<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1519382/內地製壽桃牌全蛋麵防腐劑超標三成半停售\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1519382%2F%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E8%A3%BD%E5%A3%BD%E6%A1%83%E7%89%8C%E5%85%A8%E8%9B%8B%E9%BA%B5%E9%98%B2%E8%85%90%E5%8A%91%E8%B6%85%E6%A8%99%E4%B8%89%E6%88%90%E5%8D%8A%E5%81%9C%E5%94%AE&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=a2d83148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1519382/內地製壽桃牌全蛋麵防腐劑超標三成半停售</a><br />\n2016年《鮑魚雞粉鈉爆高》<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/&hellip;/LCWSWBNQUMXMCDTRJHRT42TCUA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2FLCWSWBNQUMXMCDTRJHRT42TCUA%2F&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=db6d8206\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2FLCWSWBNQUMXMCDTRJHRT42TCUA%2F&h=21388e69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/&hellip;/LCWSWBNQUMXMCDTRJHRT42TCUA/</a><br />\n2011年《調味油，脫水菜包含塑化劑》<br />\n<a href=\"https://life.mingpao.com/general/article?issue=20110609&amp;nodeid=1508068755274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flife.mingpao.com%2Fgeneral%2Farticle%3Fissue%3D20110609%26nodeid%3D1508068755274&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=a422d0f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Flife.mingpao.com%2Fgeneral%2Farticle%3Fissue%3D20110609%26nodeid%3D1508068755274&h=5bc4f146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://life.mingpao.com/general/article?issue=20110609&amp;nodeid=1508068755274</a></span></em><br />\n<br />\n留言template：<br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"gold\">無線新聞立場偏頗、時常斷章取義，多年來誤導不少港人，懇請 貴公司轉用其他宣傳渠道，例如ViuTV及77台，以免間接資助一間為中共維穩的電視台！而在 貴公司重新審視宣傳策略前，我及我的親朋戚友將會盡量避免光顧 貴公司，敬請注意。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n1.如果你唔認同佢地既營商手法，請入facebook比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.如果你想佢地改過，請留言回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.如果你真係唔鍾意佢地，咁就唔好再買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.對志同道合既手足留言比個讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n============================================<br />\n如果想準時收到TVB任務，一定要響Facebook同Telegram follow sayno4tvb團隊（我唔係佢地團隊），又或者<strong><span class=\"red\">得閒click入呢個Post（<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059659\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059659</a>）我會盡量每日更新</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb%2F&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=d613e6ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/</a><br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno4tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno4tvb&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=e012a900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno4tvb</a><br />\n舊版抵制List: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/tvbadver\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ftvbadver&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=81dc9b2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/tvbadver</a><br />\n<br />\n最後都要重申，<span class=\"red\">我地支持自由經濟，我地同意廣告商有賣廣告既自由，但顧客都有選擇買同唔買既自由</span>，我地只會抵制無良商戶，但唔會威脅佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbYiswE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbYiswE.jpg&h=d3b9ed92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5opp9mv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5opp9mv.jpg&h=dad5157b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dVG4nk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdVG4nk5.jpg&h=69dd4c04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da7d903cf284d46e55d565b95c1c9cfdd3a7bdf7","tid":2118553,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b64b9146084d6635c10cec390b828fa1e7aec44","tid":2118553,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:50:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"565cfec440798521ebb9f126ff2e5eee5ffa38ca","tid":2118553,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:50:24.000Z","msg":"唉呀...唔好有TVB響標題呀..."},{"pid":"d53fbc5e6ae107dc943af8b8bac2ba28941df258","tid":2118553,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"565cfec440798521ebb9f126ff2e5eee5ffa38ca","tid":2118553,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:50:24.000Z","msg":"唉呀...唔好有TVB響標題呀..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:50:35.000Z","msg":",再開"},{"pid":"332dccf3728f257deec62581ce4c15104f580ff5","tid":2118553,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"同埋用錯標題...重唔重開..."},{"pid":"9ea1a803a5a6b6819aaa01983df60fda6bf87d08","tid":2118553,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da7d903cf284d46e55d565b95c1c9cfdd3a7bdf7","tid":2118553,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hk